Date: Sun, 20 Apr 2025 15:30:53 -0700
Subject: [PATCH 13/17] gcc-15: disable '-Wunterminated-string-initialization'
 entirely for now

Signed-off-by: Linus Torvalds <torvalds@xxxxxxxxxx>
---
 Makefile              | 4 ++--
 drivers/acpi/tables.c | 2 +-
 2 files changed, 3 insertions(+), 3 deletions(-)

